PeonPad
=======

PeonPad is an independent, de-branded Apple-platform port project built around
the GPLv2 Stratagus/Wargus engine. The final repository must carry the complete
GPLv2 license and the license notices of every staged dependency and libre
asset.

No Blizzard Entertainment game data, art, audio, video, map data, installer,
MPQ archive, extracted data.Wargus directory, trademarked application icon, or
signing credential may be committed to or distributed with PeonPad.

Users who choose the bring-your-own-data path must own and import their game
data themselves. Reference material under ref/ is local-only, read-only, and
not part of PeonPad.

